<h2>Daily Audit Report</h2>

<p><strong>Report Period:</strong> <%= @from_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M') %> to <%= @to_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M') %></p>

<p><strong>Employees with Status Changes:</strong> <%= @employee_count %></p>

<% if @employee_count > 0 %>
<p>This report shows employees who had status changes (appointments, terminations, transfers, etc.) during the specified time period, along with their current account statuses and any open account requests.</p>

<p>The complete report data has been attached as a CSV file for your review.</p>

<h3>Summary</h3>
<p>
  Total employees with status changes: <%= @employee_count %><br>
  Report generated: <%= Time.current.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S %Z') %>
</p>
<% else %>
<p>No employees had status changes during this time period.</p>
<% end %>

<hr>
<p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;">
  This is an automated report from the NY Senate Audit Utils system.
</p>
